      "content": "i'm a bit worried though, because if i start splitting my classes based on these things, i might accidentally be pigeonholing people. like, if i see a black client, am i expected to just assume they're built for sprinting and not give them endurance work? and does this apply to other groups too, like asians or latinos? is there a similar pattern for them in the research?",
